1
00:00:48,500 --> 00:00:52,620
=Endless Love=

2
00:00:52,620 --> 00:00:55,540
=Episode 20=

3
00:01:06,560 --> 00:01:07,239
Ke'er?

4
00:01:07,359 --> 00:01:07,840
My Lady.

5
00:01:08,000 --> 00:01:08,760
Where is Ling Xiao?

6
00:01:09,280 --> 00:01:10,439
How is he?

7
00:01:11,239 --> 00:01:12,079
Don't worry.

8
00:01:12,599 --> 00:01:14,480
Mo Shuo has taken Ling Xiao back
for treatment.

9
00:01:14,840 --> 00:01:17,120
You should be more concerned
about yourself.

10
00:01:18,040 --> 00:01:19,280
You nearly lost the child

11
00:01:20,719 --> 00:01:22,400
trying to save Ling Xiao.

12
00:01:22,840 --> 00:01:23,519
Then can you tell me

13
00:01:23,519 --> 00:01:25,200
about Ling Xiao
and the Princess of Xiling?

14
00:01:25,840 --> 00:01:27,359
Why did that person try to kill him?

15
00:01:27,879 --> 00:01:30,239
The Xiling Princess's story is no secret.

16
00:01:31,159 --> 00:01:32,200
By accident,

17
00:01:32,760 --> 00:01:33,959
the Princess saved Ling Xiao.

18
00:01:35,000 --> 00:01:36,840
But Ling Xiao, in turn,
killed the Princess

19
00:01:37,480 --> 00:01:39,000
and slaughtered all of Xiling.

20
00:01:40,599 --> 00:01:42,799
Ling Xiao is sworn enemies
with all of Xiling.

21
00:01:43,280 --> 00:01:44,200
The people of that fallen kingdom

22
00:01:44,840 --> 00:01:46,159
all see him as their mortal foe.

23
00:01:46,840 --> 00:01:49,239
So it turns out
he's the reigning King of Xiling.

24
00:01:49,680 --> 00:01:51,840
How much do I look like Mu Ruyi?

25
00:01:52,760 --> 00:01:54,200
I've never seen the Princess.

26
00:01:54,519 --> 00:01:56,000
You don't need to trouble yourself

27
00:01:56,159 --> 00:01:57,599
with things that don't involve us.

28
00:02:00,840 --> 00:02:01,879
Time for the medicine.

29
00:02:07,840 --> 00:02:09,240
(Xia Ke'er said)

30
00:02:09,919 --> 00:02:12,199
(that my mother runs a business
in the south of the city.)

31
00:02:12,840 --> 00:02:14,000
(Yet she has never shown herself.)

32
00:02:16,479 --> 00:02:19,400
(Just how much do I look like
the Princess of Xiling?)

33
00:02:22,719 --> 00:02:24,120
(How much of what Ling Xiao said)

34
00:02:25,319 --> 00:02:26,680
(is true?)

35
00:02:27,960 --> 00:02:28,879
(I wonder.)

36
00:02:31,879 --> 00:02:32,400
Your Majesty.

37
00:02:33,759 --> 00:02:34,280
Your Majesty.

38
00:02:34,919 --> 00:02:35,479
Time for your medicine.

39
00:02:42,680 --> 00:02:43,639
How is Ruyi?

40
00:02:44,039 --> 00:02:46,120
Where is she? Is she alright?

41
00:02:46,639 --> 00:02:47,879
Miss Mu is fine.

42
00:02:52,080 --> 00:02:52,639
Ling Xiao,

43
00:02:53,639 --> 00:02:55,319
do you remember who you are?

44
00:02:55,560 --> 00:02:57,000
I'm going to tell her the truth now.

45
00:02:57,560 --> 00:02:58,520
I want to confess.

46
00:03:01,000 --> 00:03:02,479
Every day you spend with Mu Ruyi,

47
00:03:02,960 --> 00:03:04,520
she's in mortal danger.

48
00:03:05,240 --> 00:03:06,800
Are you sure you want to see her now?

49
00:03:07,280 --> 00:03:08,319
We love each other,

50
00:03:09,439 --> 00:03:10,719
so we can face it together.

51
00:03:11,039 --> 00:03:13,080
Do you know who's trying to kill you?

52
00:03:13,680 --> 00:03:14,879
They're just like you.

53
00:03:15,360 --> 00:03:18,240
They are all former servants
of the Princess's mansion.

54
00:03:19,159 --> 00:03:20,080
You stopped at nothing

55
00:03:20,240 --> 00:03:21,120
for revenge,

56
00:03:21,639 --> 00:03:22,800
forging your identity,

57
00:03:23,080 --> 00:03:24,879
staying close to the Princess,

58
00:03:25,520 --> 00:03:26,719
and slaughtering her family.

59
00:03:27,759 --> 00:03:29,360
When Mu Ruyi remembers

60
00:03:30,000 --> 00:03:31,439
the pain of losing her kingdom
and her family,

61
00:03:32,400 --> 00:03:34,080
do you really think
she'll simply forget it all,

62
00:03:34,319 --> 00:03:35,439
start over with you,

63
00:03:35,639 --> 00:03:36,599
and face it together?

64
00:03:42,759 --> 00:03:44,039
My Lady, don't wait any longer.

65
00:03:45,039 --> 00:03:46,560
He hasn't shown up for so long.

66
00:03:47,360 --> 00:03:48,319
He's probably not coming.

67
00:03:48,879 --> 00:03:50,199
When he was wounded and unconscious,

68
00:03:50,479 --> 00:03:51,840
I stayed by his side.

69
00:03:53,000 --> 00:03:54,759
I scarred my hands

70
00:03:55,520 --> 00:03:56,840
to make fire and boil water for him.

71
00:03:58,280 --> 00:03:59,479
When he was poisoned and collapsed,

72
00:04:00,240 --> 00:04:02,159
I carried him out of the forest.

73
00:04:02,520 --> 00:04:04,199
I would risk my life for him!

74
00:04:04,719 --> 00:04:06,240
Yet he left without a trace,

75
00:04:06,479 --> 00:04:07,719
without a hint of longing.

76
00:04:09,159 --> 00:04:11,000
He hasn't even come to see me once.

77
00:04:16,680 --> 00:04:17,360
My Lady,

78
00:04:18,600 --> 00:04:20,519
don't grieve over someone
who isn't worth it.

79
00:04:21,160 --> 00:04:23,399
Ke'er, are you sure about my story?

80
00:04:24,160 --> 00:04:26,040
Am I just the Liu family's only daughter,
a girl whose father passed away early

81
00:04:26,399 --> 00:04:28,399
and whose mother runs a business?

82
00:04:30,040 --> 00:04:30,920
Then why

83
00:04:30,920 --> 00:04:33,240
hasn't my mother ever written to us?

84
00:04:36,839 --> 00:04:38,560
Are you hiding something from me?

85
00:04:41,959 --> 00:04:43,120
I want the truth.

86
00:04:43,839 --> 00:04:44,639
I can't just let this go.

87
00:04:45,199 --> 00:04:46,000
I'm going to see him.

88
00:04:47,639 --> 00:04:48,360
My Lady!

89
00:04:49,600 --> 00:04:51,040
If you want me to live well,

90
00:04:51,199 --> 00:04:52,199
then don't stop me.

91
00:04:52,720 --> 00:04:53,560
This is the last time.

92
00:04:54,120 --> 00:04:55,839
I want him to tell me the truth himself.

93
00:05:12,639 --> 00:05:13,279
Rushi,

94
00:05:14,639 --> 00:05:15,439
what brings you here?

95
00:05:15,839 --> 00:05:16,839
Am I not welcome here?

96
00:05:17,800 --> 00:05:19,319
Or is it because I'm a commoner,

97
00:05:19,319 --> 00:05:22,160
and I should address you
as "Your Majesty"?

98
00:05:26,319 --> 00:05:27,800
This is no place for you.

99
00:05:28,560 --> 00:05:29,199
Leave.

100
00:05:30,160 --> 00:05:31,399
Do you still remember,

101
00:05:33,399 --> 00:05:34,399
under the shooting stars,

102
00:05:34,680 --> 00:05:35,680
on New Year's Eve,

103
00:05:36,040 --> 00:05:37,120
in times of danger,

104
00:05:37,319 --> 00:05:38,399
and in moments of happiness,

105
00:05:38,680 --> 00:05:41,759
who made those so-called promises?

106
00:05:43,439 --> 00:05:45,879
It doesn't matter.

107
00:05:47,240 --> 00:05:48,360
I should remember

108
00:05:49,240 --> 00:05:50,720
an emperor's job.

109
00:05:55,839 --> 00:05:57,360
If you can so easily forget

110
00:05:57,360 --> 00:05:58,920
and break your promises to a woman,

111
00:05:59,279 --> 00:05:59,920
take back your words,

112
00:06:00,000 --> 00:06:00,639
and break your vows,

113
00:06:01,439 --> 00:06:03,240
how are you fit to be the ruler

114
00:06:03,439 --> 00:06:05,000
and command your people?

115
00:06:07,199 --> 00:06:08,480
Since you don't remember everything,

116
00:06:09,439 --> 00:06:10,639
why do you still keep this

117
00:06:10,639 --> 00:06:12,839
cheap trinket unworthy of you?

118
00:06:13,360 --> 00:06:15,480
Why are you afraid to
admit your true feelings,

119
00:06:15,920 --> 00:06:17,920
letting me suffer for no reason?

120
00:06:18,480 --> 00:06:19,759
You're despicable!

121
00:06:19,920 --> 00:06:20,680
I remember.

122
00:06:21,120 --> 00:06:21,920
I remember everything.

123
00:06:23,720 --> 00:06:24,480
We promised

124
00:06:25,000 --> 00:06:25,839
that we'd leave the past behind

125
00:06:26,600 --> 00:06:27,439
and only look to the future.

126
00:06:29,399 --> 00:06:31,439
But if you knew I'm not a good man,

127
00:06:32,000 --> 00:06:33,720
that I've done things
worthy of the scorn

128
00:06:33,800 --> 00:06:35,000
and condemnation of millions,

129
00:06:37,079 --> 00:06:38,480
would you still want to be with me,

130
00:06:39,399 --> 00:06:40,319
leaving the past behind

131
00:06:41,120 --> 00:06:42,079
and only looking to the future?

132
00:06:45,680 --> 00:06:47,680
My fate is in my own hands.

133
00:06:48,319 --> 00:06:49,920
No one's presence or absence

134
00:06:49,920 --> 00:06:51,319
can change that.

135
00:06:52,480 --> 00:06:53,759
When I said I don't care about the past,

136
00:06:54,279 --> 00:06:56,480
I truly meant it.

137
00:06:57,160 --> 00:06:59,480
Even if you've had romantic affairs,

138
00:07:00,120 --> 00:07:00,839
no matter who,

139
00:07:00,839 --> 00:07:02,639
or what entanglements you've had,

140
00:07:03,600 --> 00:07:06,160
even if you've killed or hurt others,

141
00:07:06,800 --> 00:07:08,720
whether you're a commoner

142
00:07:08,839 --> 00:07:10,120
or the reigning king,

143
00:07:10,560 --> 00:07:11,879
I only care about our future!

144
00:07:11,879 --> 00:07:13,079
Do you understand?

145
00:07:22,079 --> 00:07:23,839
I shouldn't have doubted our love.

146
00:07:25,920 --> 00:07:26,639
Sorry,

147
00:07:27,759 --> 00:07:28,519
I just

148
00:07:28,959 --> 00:07:31,399
don't want you to suffer
humiliation or danger because of me.

149
00:07:32,759 --> 00:07:34,040
Then you must hold on tight.

150
00:07:35,360 --> 00:07:36,199
Once you take my hand,

151
00:07:37,439 --> 00:07:38,959
you can't let go easily.

152
00:07:45,920 --> 00:07:46,560
Mo Shuo!

153
00:07:48,199 --> 00:07:49,319
You silly!

154
00:07:49,519 --> 00:07:51,680
Why did you bring Mu Ruyi
to the palace today?

155
00:07:51,680 --> 00:07:53,800
Don't you play dumb with me!

156
00:07:54,680 --> 00:07:56,399
Ke'er, you came to me all fired up

157
00:07:56,519 --> 00:07:58,040
just to mess with me?

158
00:07:58,319 --> 00:07:59,720
I don't think I've done anything wrong.

159
00:08:00,079 --> 00:08:01,439
Ling Xiao, that heartless villain,

160
00:08:01,839 --> 00:08:03,439
swore his love to the Princess.

161
00:08:03,759 --> 00:08:05,000
She even risked her life to save him,

162
00:08:05,480 --> 00:08:07,079
but that ungrateful wretch

163
00:08:07,240 --> 00:08:08,600
neglected her!

164
00:08:09,360 --> 00:08:10,480
I know it all!

165
00:08:10,879 --> 00:08:12,319
This was your idea.

166
00:08:12,759 --> 00:08:14,439
You're just as cold-hearted.

167
00:08:14,879 --> 00:08:15,879
Ke'er, I can explain.

168
00:08:16,319 --> 00:08:17,319
There are things I can't say.

169
00:08:17,480 --> 00:08:19,279
Something you can't say?

170
00:08:19,519 --> 00:08:20,319
How can your hardships

171
00:08:20,480 --> 00:08:22,319
compare to the Princess's?

172
00:08:22,519 --> 00:08:25,000
She carried that wretch for five li

173
00:08:25,240 --> 00:08:26,560
when he was poisoned.

174
00:08:26,839 --> 00:08:28,519
She scarred her hands gathering firewood

175
00:08:28,519 --> 00:08:29,800
just to boil him some water.

176
00:08:30,199 --> 00:08:31,920
And even in her final moments
before losing consciousness,

177
00:08:31,920 --> 00:08:33,200
she shielded him with her own body.

178
00:08:34,360 --> 00:08:35,600
Can you do that?

179
00:08:36,360 --> 00:08:38,799
Stop using lame excuses

180
00:08:38,960 --> 00:08:40,320
to break the Princess's heart!

181
00:08:40,759 --> 00:08:41,559
But Ke'er,

182
00:08:41,720 --> 00:08:43,559
it's not me who broke Mu Ruyi's heart.

183
00:08:43,960 --> 00:08:45,759
Why are you coming down so hard on me?

184
00:08:45,879 --> 00:08:46,960
Haven't you heard?

185
00:08:47,360 --> 00:08:48,720
A match made in heaven

186
00:08:48,720 --> 00:08:49,840
should not be broken.

187
00:08:50,639 --> 00:08:52,600
If you give wicked advice any more

188
00:08:52,960 --> 00:08:54,559
and shatter the Princess's heart again,

189
00:08:55,279 --> 00:08:56,840
I'll kill you!

190
00:08:59,799 --> 00:09:00,879
Alright, Ke'er. I promise you.

191
00:09:01,399 --> 00:09:03,039
I won't meddle in their affairs anymore.

192
00:09:03,840 --> 00:09:05,440
Their destiny

193
00:09:05,879 --> 00:09:07,440
is theirs to decide.

194
00:09:45,639 --> 00:09:46,360
Ke'er,

195
00:09:46,519 --> 00:09:49,200
this place feels so familiar.

196
00:09:53,240 --> 00:09:54,000
My Lady,

197
00:09:55,120 --> 00:09:56,600
are you absolutely sure about this?

198
00:09:59,399 --> 00:10:01,279
The palace is a place of watchful eyes

199
00:10:01,559 --> 00:10:02,440
and treacherous schemes.

200
00:10:03,240 --> 00:10:04,840
It's not as simple as you can imagine,

201
00:10:05,399 --> 00:10:07,919
nor as carefree as the world outside.

202
00:10:08,320 --> 00:10:09,399
Since I've made my decision,

203
00:10:10,200 --> 00:10:11,120
I won't regret it.

204
00:10:12,600 --> 00:10:13,200
Alright.

205
00:10:14,360 --> 00:10:16,440
My greatest wish in this life

206
00:10:16,720 --> 00:10:18,279
is for you to live worry-free

207
00:10:18,279 --> 00:10:19,600
and do what you love.

208
00:10:20,000 --> 00:10:21,360
Since you've made up your mind,

209
00:10:21,559 --> 00:10:23,000
I'll stay by your side

210
00:10:23,240 --> 00:10:23,960
and keep you safe.

211
00:10:24,440 --> 00:10:25,039
Ke'er,

212
00:10:25,960 --> 00:10:27,399
thank you for keeping me safe.

213
00:10:28,000 --> 00:10:28,679
From now on,

214
00:10:29,360 --> 00:10:30,720
let me be the one to protect you.

215
00:10:32,679 --> 00:10:35,240
This is all my duty.

216
00:10:36,320 --> 00:10:39,200
There's no such thing as "duty".

217
00:10:39,559 --> 00:10:41,039
You must live for yourself.

218
00:10:41,720 --> 00:10:42,440
My Lady,

219
00:10:43,039 --> 00:10:43,960
for all these years,

220
00:10:44,799 --> 00:10:46,960
I've already come to
see you as my family.

221
00:10:48,559 --> 00:10:49,919
After all we've been through,

222
00:10:51,279 --> 00:10:52,360
I'm just worried about you.

223
00:10:53,720 --> 00:10:55,120
Thank you, Ke'er.

224
00:10:55,879 --> 00:10:57,720
You never ask
whether I'm right or wrong.

225
00:10:58,320 --> 00:10:59,919
You just stand by me, without question.

226
00:11:02,159 --> 00:11:04,159
Once this is all over,

227
00:11:05,039 --> 00:11:05,840
I hope

228
00:11:06,320 --> 00:11:08,519
you can also pursue your own happiness.

229
00:11:09,360 --> 00:11:10,360
You don't have to keep sacrificing

230
00:11:10,679 --> 00:11:12,639
and changing for me anymore.

231
00:11:13,080 --> 00:11:13,600
Do you agree?

232
00:11:15,000 --> 00:11:15,519
I agree.

233
00:11:16,200 --> 00:11:17,240
Then, from now on,

234
00:11:17,840 --> 00:11:19,240
let's live freely

235
00:11:19,799 --> 00:11:20,679
and follow our hearts.

236
00:11:24,360 --> 00:11:25,000
Your Majesty,

237
00:11:25,480 --> 00:11:27,000
are you feeling unwell today?

238
00:11:30,919 --> 00:11:32,399
After what happened in the forest,

239
00:11:32,799 --> 00:11:34,320
I've been having headaches.

240
00:11:34,480 --> 00:11:35,519
Every time it comes,

241
00:11:35,879 --> 00:11:37,679
I remember things from further back.

242
00:11:38,559 --> 00:11:40,440
Your Majesty, that's good news.

243
00:11:41,039 --> 00:11:42,679
That means your memory is coming back.

244
00:11:44,320 --> 00:11:46,200
Your Majesty,
a carrier pigeon from Chancellor Zhao

245
00:11:46,360 --> 00:11:47,120
was intercepted.

246
00:11:58,080 --> 00:12:00,320
Your Majesty, what was it
that made you so angry?

247
00:12:06,360 --> 00:12:08,279
Learning that my beloved daughter
has been wronged,

248
00:12:09,000 --> 00:12:11,159
I will surely seek justice for her.

249
00:12:11,840 --> 00:12:13,159
If he cannot judge fairly,

250
00:12:13,639 --> 00:12:15,279
then I shall seek justice myself.

251
00:12:16,360 --> 00:12:18,360
He dares to scheme
and threaten in secret!

252
00:12:19,240 --> 00:12:21,399
How dare he!

253
00:12:21,759 --> 00:12:22,320
Your Majesty,

254
00:12:23,399 --> 00:12:24,799
if you don't release Zhao Sisi,

255
00:12:25,440 --> 00:12:27,039
I fear Chancellor Zhao

256
00:12:27,039 --> 00:12:28,240
will not spare Miss Mu.

257
00:12:33,759 --> 00:12:34,559
For Ruyi's sake,

258
00:12:35,679 --> 00:12:36,600
I have no choice.

259
00:12:43,679 --> 00:12:45,600
Shattered glass blooms
like a broken dream.

260
00:12:46,120 --> 00:12:47,639
Cold rain on the windowpane

261
00:12:48,320 --> 00:12:50,759
severs the last strands of yearning.

262
00:12:50,960 --> 00:12:52,879
I recall the warmth we once shared,

263
00:12:54,120 --> 00:12:55,759
but tears have soaked my pillow,

264
00:12:56,600 --> 00:12:58,519
and the old days are lost to me.

265
00:13:02,600 --> 00:13:04,200
Shattered glass blooms
like a broken dream?

266
00:13:05,360 --> 00:13:06,360
Jing Liuli?

267
00:13:07,600 --> 00:13:09,000
How could she have composed

268
00:13:09,159 --> 00:13:11,120
such sorrowful yet tender words?

269
00:13:12,000 --> 00:13:14,480
I knew that I bore some resemblance

270
00:13:14,679 --> 00:13:15,840
to the Princess of Xiling,

271
00:13:16,480 --> 00:13:17,639
but I never expected

272
00:13:18,039 --> 00:13:20,159
that I would look so much
like Jing Liuli too.

273
00:13:21,360 --> 00:13:23,279
What is going on here?
